metadata.name: Unravel People's UNDEAD
metadata.description: Abbreviation for unravel people's UNDEAD, which represents an inactive state of pUNDEAD. User can participate in a new UNDEAD acquirement subscription and will receive unravel people's UNDEAD as credit. upUNDEAD can be claimed into pUNDEAD when the subscription successfully acquires a new UNDEAD.
